                <h1>Arts and Sciences Council considers new certificate program, plagiarism report</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/d7b8b0da-b95c-4f78-9098-2731f41a11b5.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="Council&#x20;Chair&#x20;Thomas&#x20;Robisheaux&#x20;at&#x20;a&#x20;previous&#x20;Arts&#x20;and&#x20;Sciences&#x20;Council&#x20;meeting." class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            Council Chair Thomas Robisheaux at a previous Arts and Sciences Council meeting.

